Of course, that makes this trio all the more special, and this first effort perhaps the most special of all. It may be an eyefilling, mindbending martial arts tale of two royal princes battling for the rightful recovery of the throne, but its also a party, where Tang invites two cinematographers, three editors, and no less than five other choreographer friends to almost literally shoot the works.
